title: Breaking Down the End of ‘Game of Thrones’ | The Watch
description:
The end of ‘Game of Thrones’ was a tale of two finales (1:06). We parse through the ending of the show (6:59), attempt to tie up loose ends (32:30), and make predictions for what will fill the vacuum left by ‘Game of Thrones’ (59:06).

Hosts: Chris Ryan and Andy Greenwald
